headline: Genuine Parts Company to Present at the UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference
summary: Genuine Parts Company (NYSE: GPC), a leading global service provider of automotive and industrial replacement parts and value-added solutions, announced today that Will Stengel, President & CEO, and Bert Nappier, EVP & CFO, will present at the 14th Annual UBS Global Consumer and Retail Conference at 9:00 a.m. ET on Wednesday, March 12, 2025.
